   - The `inlineComments` array and rule-code suffixes stay as-is. The linked leading-location forms are preserved, so the existing negative guards (banning backticked `` `src/webhooks/payment.ts:62` ``) still hold.
   - verify: the example contains `[docs/webhooks.md](<pr-blob-url>/docs/webhooks.md)` (summary, no line), `[src/webhooks/config.ts](<pr-blob-url>/src/webhooks/config.ts)` (mid-description, no line), and a backticked `` `retry*` `` specimen.

